headline: PGIM Private Capital Provides $14.9B of Senior Debt and Junior Capital Globally in 2024
summary: CHICAGO, March 03, 2025--PGIM Private Capital provided $14.9 billion of senior debt and junior capital to more than 238 middle-market companies and projects globally in 2024.

headline: Prudential Financial: Best Days May Be Yet Ahead
summary: Prudential increased its revenue from $57.1 billion in FY 2015 to $70.4 billion in FY 2024, a compound annual growth rate of 2.4%.
